{"tid":398440,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"仆佢個街阿 疑似被吉野家呃我錢","createTime":"2017-09-13T08:00:36.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-14T03:52:40.000Z","uid":69799,"like":2,"dislike":203,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e5a2969f680bac35b3aa403846f216d40da782e6","tid":398440,"uid":69799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T08:00:36.000Z","msg":"甘今日我就諗緊食個23蚊脆弱雞腿包餐好定22蚊燒味飯好<br />\n見今日心情靚 阿媽又醒左50蚊 一於豪豪地歎個吉野家下午茶 <br />\n甘就叫個細牛肉飯同細雞肉飯啦 咁轉可樂要加2蚊 <br />\n甘我老閪都飲日本茶啦<br />\n我比100蚊 阿佢老母找我48.5<br />\n外賣1細牛1細雞究竟幾錢 吉野家人入急問<br />\n甘我即刻沖返屋企上yoshinoya官網睇幾錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n阿屌 佢有圖無價錢<br />\n宜家懷疑吉野家黑箱作業 欺騙廣大消費者<br />\n我好懷疑樓下個死intern收銀收多左我錢<br />\n好能貴阿e餐 屌<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2310eeeabeb1fad67b9e0521a637593340dba2bd","tid":398440,"uid":10608,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T08:01:51.000Z","msg":"0。1/10<br />\n<br />\n不太切合主題"},{"pid":"6a9edb3a8f2fefe9b3570a354f6a2c4116089aac","tid":398440,"uid":15309,"like":32,"dislike":0,"score":32,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T08:02:35.000Z","msg":"甘撚夠未<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/30.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56bb6a20905c7ffe730b64c24031dcba0a537306","tid":398440,"uid":31254,"like":54,"dislike":2,"score":52,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T08:04:05.000Z","msg":"我叫左去買個白汁 咁d飯有d雞皇 就$26蚊<br />\n<br />\n條友問我要唔要加飲野黎飲 我唔洗講啦 就要百事 點知佢話百事有可樂<br />\n<br />\n我都唔知佢up咩鳩 跟住我話唔要野飲 佢話30蚊 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我話唔要 跟住佢話我係咪睇電視<br />\n<br />\n屌佢老味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> on99<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4482f0c62e60e4a446fbf4567ea97af73f2762e5","tid":398440,"uid":65587,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T08:06:22.000Z","msg":"吉野家良心企業嚟 唔會呃你錢賺你錢<br />\n但求開開心心打